[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……よし、いったん休憩にしよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01164",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ふー……えへへ、歌も踊りも\n結構いい感じになってきたんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01165",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "いーや、まだまだね。\nイザナ、あんたは振りも歌も走りすぎ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01166",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "はぁーい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01167",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "本番まであと３日かあ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01168",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "心配はいらぬ。現時点でこの完成度ならば、\n本番までには完璧に仕上げられるはず",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01169",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ううん、そうじゃなくて。この三人で\n一緒にいられるのもあとそれだけなんだと思って……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01170",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01171",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01172",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "あ、ごめんね！　湿っぽい感じにしちゃって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01173",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "まあ、いいんじゃないの。少しくらいは。\n言ってることは本当なんだし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01174",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……なら、湿っぽい空気に便乗して、\n少し話をしてもよいか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01175",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "なになに？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01176",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "かしこまって話すのも小恥ずかしいのだが……\n二人には、改めて感謝を伝えたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01177",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ヨハナ、イザナ。本当にありがとう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01178",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "売れないアイドルだった拙者が、これほど大きな舞台に\n臨めるのは、二人の力あってこそでござる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01179",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それはアタシも同じだよ。\n鬼門にはいっぱい助けられたもん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01180",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ね、ヨハナもそう思うでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01181",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そ、そうね……確かに、あんたのアドバイスに\n助けられたこともなくはなかったし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01182",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あんたがいなかったら『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』は\nまとまらなかったと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01183",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "鬼門がリーダーでよかったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01184",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うん！　ありがとね、リーダー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01185",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "二人とも……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01186",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "正直、手の掛かるメンバーだったのは確かでござるな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01187",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "むむ……子ども扱いして！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01188",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "しかし、この三人でよかった。それは確かだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01189",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（……拙者が辞めた後、\n　『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』はどうなるのだろう）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01190",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（二人は、どうするつもりなのだろう）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01191",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（……いや、終わった後のことを話すには早すぎるか）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01192",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……いいライブにしよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01193",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01194",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ええ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01195",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]